ZH: 我的胃不太好，消化功能不太好。
EN: My stomach is not very good, my digestion is not very good.

ZH: 这个食物对我来说很难消化。
EN: This food is hard for me to digest.

ZH: 吃多了油腻的东西会让人容易消化不良。
EN: Eating too much greasy food can easily cause indigestion.

ZH: 好的消化能加速新陈代谢。
EN: Good digestion can boost metabolism.

ZH: 长时间坐着工作不利于消化。
EN: Sitting for long periods of time is not good for digestion.

ZH: 健康的饮食习惯对消化系统很重要。
EN: Healthy eating habits are important for the digestive system.

ZH: 食物要经过消化才能被身体吸收。
EN: Food needs to be digested in order to be absorbed by the body.

ZH: 快速吞咽食物会影响消化过程。
EN: Swallowing food quickly can affect the digestion process.

ZH: 在饭后散步有助于消化。
EN: Taking a walk after meals helps with digestion.

ZH: 加入酸奶可以改善消化问题。
EN: Adding yogurt can improve digestion issues.

ZH: 常喝一些消化茶有助于消化和排毒。
EN: Drinking digestive tea regularly helps with digestion and detoxification.

